trans-unit.source: Represents a dialog box that allows the user to choose a type.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma caixa de diálogo que permite ao usuário escolher um tipo.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] This class prompts the user to browse a list of Windows Workflow Foundation and .NET Framework namespaces and their contained types and select a single type.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Essa classe solicita ao usuário para procurar uma lista de namespaces do Windows Workflow Foundation e do .NET Framework e seus tipos independentes e selecionar um único tipo.

trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.IServiceProvider>de que a caixa de diálogo obtém serviços.</xref:System.IServiceProvider>

trans-unit.source: Gets the component to associate with the type browser dialog box.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o componente para associar a caixa de diálogo de navegador de tipo.

trans-unit.source: If the property returns a valid value--anything other than a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic)--the component is added to <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>.
trans-unit.target: Se a propriedade retornará um valor válido – algo diferente de uma referência nula (`Nothing` no Visual Basic) – o componente é adicionado à <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>

trans-unit.source: This property is required because <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog> implements <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.
trans-unit.target: Esta propriedade é necessária porque <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>implementa <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>

trans-unit.source: For <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.ComponentModel.ISite.Component%2A> always returns a null reference (`Nothing`).
trans-unit.target: Para <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.ComponentModel.ISite.Component%2A>sempre retorna uma referência nula (`Nothing`).</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.ComponentModel.ISite.Component%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the type browser dialog is in design mode.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um valor que indica se a caixa de diálogo de navegador de tipo está no modo de design.

trans-unit.source: This property is required because <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog> implements <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.
trans-unit.target: Esta propriedade é necessária porque <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>implementa <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>

trans-unit.source: For <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.ComponentModel.ISite.DesignMode%2A> always returns `true`.
trans-unit.target: Para <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.ComponentModel.ISite.DesignMode%2A>sempre retorna `true`.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.ComponentModel.ISite.DesignMode%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>

trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o nome do componente associado com a caixa de diálogo de navegador de tipo.

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the service object for the specified type.
trans-unit.target: Recupera o objeto de serviço para o tipo especificado.

trans-unit.source: If `serviceType` is of type <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.ITypeProvider>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.IServiceProvider.GetService%2A> returns a service object.
trans-unit.target: Se `serviceType` é do tipo <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.ITypeProvider>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.IServiceProvider.GetService%2A>retorna um objeto de serviço.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.IServiceProvider.GetService%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.ITypeProvider>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.IServiceProvider.GetService%2A> returns a null reference (`Nothing`).
trans-unit.target: Caso contrário, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.IServiceProvider.GetService%2A>retorna uma referência nula (`Nothing`).</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.IServiceProvider.GetService%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Type> of service object to retrieve.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Type>do objeto de serviço para recuperar.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: A service object of type serviceType, or a null reference ( in Visual Basic) if there is no service object of type serviceType.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto de serviço do tipo serviceType , ou uma referência nula ( no Visual Basic) se não houver nenhum objeto de serviço do tipo serviceType .
